Clerics who take the Darkness domain have heightened senses and are granted spells that master darkness and blind others.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Blind-fight: The cleric receives an extra chance to overcome an invisible opponent's concealment.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>ghostly visage (1), blindness and deafness (2), shadow conjuration (5), power word blind (7), and power word kill (9)</i>.